snippet.title: Laika: Aged Through Blood - Official Announcement Trailer | Future Games Show 2023
snippet.description:
Brainwash Gang revealed the trailer for Laika: Aged Through Blood, a Western-inspired motorvania where a mother coyote warrior from an oppressed tribe descends on an endless path of vengeance through a post-apocalyptic wasteland to take back what her people lost. Laika: Aged Through Blood is coming soon to PC, PlayStation 4, PlayStation 5, Xbox Series X/S, Xbox One, and Nintendo Switch, with a Steam demo launching June 19.

#SummerOfGaming
